<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
	<title>아름in - 로그인</title>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

	<!-- My CSS -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/css/login.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/lib/library.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
		integrity="sha384-KyZXEAg3QhqLMpG8r+8fhAXLRk2vvoC2f3B09zVXn8CA5QIVfZOJ3BCsw2P0p/We" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>

<div class="modal fade" id="Notice" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1"
	aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
	<div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
		<div class="modal-content">
			<div class="modal-header">
				<h5 class="modal-title font-c">공지사항</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="modal-body font-n">
				<p>
					서비스를 이제 막 시작했습니다!<br />
					아직 수많은 버그가 있을 수 있습니다<br />
				</p> <br />
				<p>
					버그 발견시 20709 박성훈에게 제보해주세요!<br />
					<a href="https://open.kakao.com/me/koderpark">버그 제보 링크</a><br />
				</p> <br />
				<p>
					회원가입 이후에 로그인이 가능합니다<br />
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="modal-footer">
				<button type="button" class="btn btn-white font-c" data-bs-dismiss="modal">닫기</button>
				<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary font-c"
					onclick="location.href = '/register';">회원가입</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<body class="bg-light bodyalign">
	<div class="smallbox">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row flex-row-reverse">
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-5 padd">
					<div class="box r4 bg-white wrapper font-c border-a">
						<div class="d-flex justify-content-center p-img">
							<img src="/src/img/areumgo-logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo">
							<img src="/src/img/title_black.png" alt="logo" class="logo">
						</div>
						<form action="/entry" method="POST" class="bottomalign">
							<input type="text" name="id" placeholder="아이디" class="form r2 field" autocomplete="off">
							<input type="password" name="pw" placeholder="비밀번호" class="form r2 field"
								autocomplete="off">
							<button class="form r2 button font-c mt-2rem">로그인</button>
							<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
								<a href="/register" class="regi font-n">회원가입</a>
							</div>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-5 padd">
					<div class="box r4 bg-colored font-c border-a d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
						<h1 class="h0 p-txt">오늘의 급식</h1>
						<div id="carousel" class="h-100 carousel slide font-n" data-bs-ride="carousel">
							<div class="carousel-inner">
								<div class="carousel-item active p-meal">
									<h3>
										중식<br>
										<%- ml %>
									</h3>
								</div>
								<div class="carousel-item p-meal">
									<h3>
										석식<br>
										<%- md %>
									</h3>
								</div>
							</div>
							<button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button"
								data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
								<span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
								<span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
							</button>
							<button class="carousel-control-next" type="button"
								data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide="next">
								<span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
								<span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
							</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

<!-- Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="../../src/lib/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
	integrity="sha384-cn7l7gDp0eyniUwwAZgrzD06kc/tftFf19TOAs2zVinnD/C7E91j9yyk5//jjpt/"
	crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<script>
	var myModal = new bootstrap.Modal(document.getElementById('Notice'));
	myModal.show();
</script>

</html>